# Create .gitignore in your project root
```

Open VS Code, create a new file called `.gitignore` in the project root and paste this:
```
# Data — never push to GitHub (too large)
data/dicom/
data/processed/
data/raw/*.zip

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Outputs
outputs/*.pth
outputs/*.ckpt

# Env
.env
wandb/